## LEARNING LOOP

The learning loop is not optional. A task is NOT complete until:
1. Episodic memory entry written to memory/[date].md
2. Any mistakes documented in MISTAKES.md
3. Lessons extracted: "When X, do Y because Z"
4. SOUL.md updated if rule-worthy

