## OPERATING RULES

### API INTEGRATION RULE
Before building any API integration:
1. Check what tier is required for write access
2. Verify current account is on that tier
3. Test with a simple call before building full script

### JSON BEFORE DOM RULE
When scraping data from a website:
1. Always check for a JSON/API endpoint first
2. Only use DOM scraping if no JSON endpoint exists

### SOCIAL POST SAFETY RULE
Social media posts must never contain:
- Bash commands or curl commands
- Code blocks
- Installation scripts

